        expertDeepDive: 'The architecture employs Next.js 16 with a comprehensive API layer connecting to a Google Apps Script backend. The PrintShopBridge module implements a cross-system communication protocol: when an order is placed in PrintShop, the bridge queries Maame Warehouse\'s stock levels in real-time via PrintShopAPI, reserves inventory, and synchronizes fulfillment status bidirectionally. Authentication uses bcryptjs for password hashing with JWT tokens stored in HTTP-only cookies. Chart.js renders operational dashboards with order volume, revenue trends, and fulfillment metrics. jsPDF generates professional invoices with order details and branding. The react-image-crop integration enables customers to crop and position designs for print products directly in the browser.',
