        expertDeepDive: 'The multi-tenant architecture isolates school data at the spreadsheet level — each school\'s data lives in its own Google Sheets workbook, provisioned automatically through the ICUNI Labs Cockpit. The 5-tier governance model is implemented as cascading permission sets: T0 members can view content and update their own profile, T1 club members gain recognition but no administrative privileges, T2 year group executives manage their cohort, T3 school administrators control school-wide settings and content, and T4 platform staff (ICUNI Labs) have cross-school access for engineering and support. The newsletter editorial workflow implements draft → editor review → admin approval → scheduled publish, with email delivery integration. The group board supports threaded comments with emoji reactions — implementing a simplified social interaction layer without the engagement-farming mechanics of traditional social media. Built on React 19.2 + Vite 7 + Tailwind with Zustand for state management.',
