        solution: 'Architected Browser History Recap to process all data entirely within the user\'s local environment. The tool parses browser SQLite databases using sql.js (WebAssembly SQLite), generates D3.js word clouds from browsing patterns, renders Recharts time-series visualizations of browsing habits over time, supports Google OAuth for optional cloud preference sync, and exports complete reports as PDFs via jsPDF + html2canvas. Zero data ever leaves the user\'s machine.',
